  <brief_title>Effect of Casodex on Tumour Hypoxia - Prostate Cancer</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Study of the Effect of Neoadjuvant Bicalutamide (Casodex) on Tumour Hypoxia in Patients With Clinically Localized Prostate Cancer</official_title>
